<i>noun</i>: 일광욕 [일광뇩] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>일광욕 [일광뇩]</dt><br>
<dd>sunbathing</dd><br>
<dd>병을 치료하거나 건강을 지키려고 온몸을 드러내어 햇빛을 쬠. 또는 그런 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Exposure of a person's body to the sun to treat an illness or improve his/her health; or such an act.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>